# Orderly Design System

A premium legal tech design system inspired by Harvey.ai and Legora.com. Professional, trustworthy, and modern.

## Brand Identity

**Orderly** - Legal work, without limits.

- Logo: Abstract interconnected curves (organization/flow)
- Primary Color: Deep royal blue gradient
- Aesthetic: Premium, enterprise-grade, trustworthy

