### Brand Gradient

```css
/* Primary brand gradient - use for heroes, CTAs */
--gradient-brand: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1B7A 0%, #1E40AF 50%, #2563EB 100%);

/* Subtle gradient for cards/sections */
--gradient-subtle: linear-gradient(180deg, hsl(var(--background)) 0%, hsl(var(--muted)) 100%);
```

### Usage Rules

```typescript
// ✅ Use semantic tokens
<div className="bg-background text-foreground">
<Button className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground">

// ✅ Use brand gradient for heroes
<section className="bg-gradient-brand">

// ❌ Don't use raw hex values
<div style={{ background: '#1E3A8A' }}>
```

